verbose_text: Moreover, prediction of bioinformatics software and luciferase reporter assay identified that nitric oxide synthase 3 (NOS3) is a target gene of miR-134; thereby, further experiments showed that miR-134 can attenuate the expression of NOS3 and overexpressed NOS3 was capable to intensify the influence relying on miR-134 inhibitor in myocardial I/R injury.
